BiMaTo
======

|DOI| |GPLv3 license| |PyPI version shields.io| |Documentation Status|

.. |DOI| image:: https://zenodo.org/badge/DOI/10.1038/s41598-019-44764-5.svg
   :target: https://doi.org/10.1038/s41598-019-44764-5

